+# Fabro Racer Mini — Final Implementation Plan
+
+## Overview
+
+Build a 3D voxel kart racer as purely static files (HTML + JS + CSS). Three.js loaded via CDN import map. No build step, no Node.js, no TypeScript, no frameworks. The game works by serving `output/` from any static file server.
+
+This plan synthesizes the Opus and GPT implementation plans, selecting the most detailed and correct approach for each module.
+
+---
+
+## File Structure
+
+```
+output/
+  index.html                      — Single HTML entry point, importmap for Three.js CDN
+  css/
+    style.css                     — Menu, HUD, and overlay styling
+  js/
+    main.js                       — Entry point: bootstrap scene, game loop, state machine
+    game.js                       — Race state machine, lap/checkpoint tracking, position calc, results
+    physics.js                    — Arcade kart physics: velocity, acceleration, steering, collision response
+    drift.js                      — Drift state machine, charge tiers, boost application
+    input.js                      — Keyboard input manager (keydown/keyup polling)
+    camera.js                     — Chase camera, drift offset, boost FOV, countdown/finish cameras
+    tracks/
+      trackBase.js                — Shared track utilities: spline eval, road mesh extrusion, checkpoint planes, off-road test, wall generation
+      sunsetCircuit.js            — Track 1: control points, segments, hazards, scenery, item-box positions, AI splines
+      crystalCaverns.js           — Track 2: control points, segments, hazards, scenery, item-box positions, AI splines
+    characters/
+      characterData.js            — 4 characters: stats, AI personality, color palettes, derived stat helpers
+      kartBuilder.js              — Voxel kart mesh generator (merged BoxGeometry composites)
+    items/
+      itemSystem.js               — Item box spawning, inventory, distribution tables, collection detection
+      sparkBomb.js                — Spark Bomb projectile logic + mesh
+      slickPuddle.js              — Slick Puddle drop logic + mesh
+      turboCell.js                — Turbo Cell instant-use logic + VFX
+    ai/
+      aiDriver.js                 — CPU driver: spline following, steering, difficulty tuning, item use, overtaking, rubber banding
+      racingSplines.js            — Per-track authored racing lines, variation splines, drift-zone markers, hazard avoidance
+    ui/
+      menuSystem.js               — Pre-race flow: title → track select → char select → difficulty/options → start
+      hud.js                      — In-race HUD: position, lap, timer, speed, drift bar, item slot, minimap canvas
+      pauseMenu.js                — Pause overlay (resume/restart/quit)
+      results.js                  — Post-race results screen
+    audio/
+      audioManager.js             — Web Audio API context, master/music/sfx gain nodes
+      synthSfx.js                 — Procedural SFX generators (engine, drift, boost, items, collisions, countdown)
+      musicLoop.js                — Per-track procedural music loops
+    utils/
+      mathUtils.js                — lerp, clamp, remap, angle helpers, point-in-polygon
+      voxelUtils.js               — Shared voxel geometry builder: merge boxes, instanced mesh, particle pool
+```
+
+**Total: 26 JS modules + 1 HTML + 1 CSS = 28 files.** No external images, no audio files, no build artifacts.
