+  - Pixel: sleek low body, no visible wheels (flat hover plates), neon trim emissive edges, pointed ears, tail of articulated cubes (~50 boxes). Purple/cyan.
+- Character figure on top: torso, head, arms from ~20-30 boxes
+- All merged via `voxelUtils.buildMergedBoxes()` for draw call efficiency (one draw call per kart)
+- Bounding box for physics: 2×1.5×3 units (spec §4.2), stored as metadata
+- Also export `buildCharacterPreview(characterDef)` for menu display
