+## Phase 5: Items + Pickups
+
+**Goal:** Item boxes on tracks, 3 items with full effects, position-weighted distribution per spec §7.
+
+**Files created:** `js/items/itemSystem.js`, `js/items/sparkBomb.js`, `js/items/slickPuddle.js`, `js/items/turboCell.js`
+
+### 5.1 `js/items/itemSystem.js`
+
+**Item box rendering:**
+- Floating spinning cubes (1.5×1.5×1.5) with `?` symbol on faces (multi-colored BoxGeometry)
+- Rotate on Y continuously (0.5 rad/s), bob up/down with sine wave (amplitude 0.3, 1 Hz)
+- When collected: disappear, respawn after 5s with fade-in
+- Placement: read `itemBoxClusters` from track data. 4 boxes per cluster, evenly spaced across road width, 1.5u above road.
+
+**Collection detection:** Sphere check (2u radius) against all kart positions. Only triggers if kart has no held item.
+
+**Distribution table (spec §7.1):**
+| Position | Spark Bomb | Slick Puddle | Turbo Cell |
+|---|---|---|---|
+| 1st | 15% | 50% | 35% |
+| 2nd | 30% | 35% | 35% |
+| 3rd | 40% | 25% | 35% |
+| 4th | 50% | 15% | 35% |
+
+Roll weighted random on collection.
+
+**Inventory:** Each kart holds at most 1 item. `kart.heldItem = 'sparkBomb' | 'slickPuddle' | 'turboCell' | null`.
+
+**Item usage:** Player presses E/X → `useItem(kart, item)`. AI decides via personality logic.
+
+**Active items array:** Track all in-world item entities (flying bombs, dropped puddles). Update positions, check collisions, remove expired each frame.
+
+**Immunity rules:** Stunned karts immune to additional stun. Invincible karts immune to damage. Items usable during invincibility.
+
+### 5.2 `js/items/sparkBomb.js`
+- **Fire:** Projectile launched forward at kart speed + 15 u/s. Follows road surface Y.
+- **Travel:** Straight line (locked heading) for up to 3s or 60 units. Slight homing toward nearest kart ahead within 15° cone.
+- **Visual:** Glowing yellow cube + electric particle trail
+- **On kart hit:** Spin target for 0.8s, zero speed, cancel drift. Explosion particle burst.
+- **On wall hit:** Explode harmlessly.
+- **On timeout:** Drop to ground, explode after 1s as proximity mine (2u trigger radius). Despawn.
+
+### 5.3 `js/items/slickPuddle.js`
+- **Drop:** Placed 3 units behind kart on road surface.
+- **Visual:** Flat green translucent circle (2.5u radius)
+- **On contact** (any kart including dropper after 1s grace period): 360° spin 0.8s, -30% speed, cancel drift, puddle disappears.
+- **Lifetime:** 12s then fades out
+
+### 5.4 `js/items/turboCell.js`
+- **Use:** Instant application, no projectile
+- **Effect:** 1.4× speed multiplier for 1.5s (equivalent to Tier 2 drift boost)
+- **Stacking:** Extends timer if already boosting, uses higher multiplier
+- **Visual:** Cyan particle burst around kart
+
+### 5.5 Validation Gate
+Collect items from boxes (boxes disappear and respawn). Use with E key. Spark Bomb fires forward and spins targets. Puddle drops behind and spins contacts. Turbo Cell gives instant boost. `render_game_to_text()` reports held item and active items correctly. Distribution varies by position.
