+## Phase Execution Order & Dependencies
+
+```
+Phase 1: Scaffold & Scene
+  └── index.html, style.css, main.js, input.js, mathUtils.js, voxelUtils.js
+  └── Depends on: nothing
+
+Phase 2: Track Geometry + Rendering
+  └── trackBase.js, sunsetCircuit.js, crystalCaverns.js
+  └── Depends on: Phase 1 (scene, utils)
+
+Phase 3: Kart Physics + Driving Model
+  └── characterData.js, kartBuilder.js, physics.js, camera.js
+  └── Depends on: Phase 1 (input), Phase 2 (track surface/walls)
+
+Phase 4: Drift/Boost System
+  └── drift.js
+  └── Depends on: Phase 3 (physics integration)
+
+Phase 5: Items + Pickups
+  └── itemSystem.js, sparkBomb.js, slickPuddle.js, turboCell.js
+  └── Depends on: Phase 3 (kart state), Phase 2 (item box placement)
+
+Phase 6: AI Opponents
+  └── aiDriver.js, racingSplines.js
+  └── Depends on: Phase 3 (physics), Phase 4 (drift), Phase 5 (items)
+
+Phase 7: HUD + Menus + Audio
+  └── game.js, menuSystem.js, hud.js, pauseMenu.js, results.js,
+      audioManager.js, synthSfx.js, musicLoop.js
+  └── Depends on: Phases 2-6 (all gameplay systems)
+
+Phase 8: Polish + Textures + Visual Effects
+  └── Particles, hazards, visual polish, performance optimization, final wiring
+  └── Depends on: all previous phases
+```
+
+**Critical path:** 1 → 2 → 3 → 4 → 6 → 7 → 8 must be sequential. Phases 4 and 5 can run in parallel (both depend on 3, not each other). Phase 7 combines UI, audio, and the game state machine since they all depend on complete gameplay systems and are tightly coupled in integration.
